4. --import requirement: New addons require godot --headless --import before first GUT run.
5. -gdir flag: GUT 9.6.0 uses -gdir (not -gdirs).
6. JSON key ordering: Godot's JSON.stringify may reorder keys alphabetically.
7. Godot version deviation: Using 4.6.2 (spec references 4.5); APIs stable across 4.x.

